	<p pid="a.37.5/1">The remuneration and time commitments of chairs/members of all Northern Ireland Office public bodies are published each year in the Northern Ireland Office departmental report. Similar information for bodies sponsored by Northern Ireland's 11 government departments is published in their annual <I>Public Appointments Annual Report</I>. Copies of the latest versions of both these reports are available from the Library of the House and can be found on the Internet at <a href="http://www.nio.gov.uk/nio_departmental_report_2006.pdf">www.nio.gov.uk/nio_departmental_report_2006.pdf</a> and <a href="http://www.ofmdfmni.gov.uk/public-appointments">www.ofmdfmni.gov.uk/public-appointments</a>.</p>
